                    <span class="highlight-tag">Laravel Specialist</span>
                    <span class="highlight-tag">TypeScript Expert</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="pitch-summary">I deliver enterprise-grade solutions that reduced deployment time by 40% and achieved 90%+ test coverage. From architecting RESTful APIs to collaborating with cross-functional teams using Agile methodologies, I bridge the gap between complex technical requirements and business outcomes.</p>
